# Normalize all text files to LF on commit AND in the working tree.
# Overrides each contributor's core.autocrlf, so Git for Windows checkouts
# don't silently flip line endings and trigger Prettier reformatting churn.
# `text=auto` lets Git detect binaries by content; explicit binary rules
# below cover common assets where the heuristic might guess wrong.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binaries — never touch line endings, never diff inline.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
